### Post entry
POST {{apiurl}}/entries
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "entry_date": "2026-04-08",
    "mood": "happy",
    "weight_now": 75,
    "sleep_hours": 8,
    "notes": "Feeling great today!"
}

### GET entries by user id
GET {{apiurl}}/entries/19
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET latest entry from user
GET {{apiurl}}/entries/latest/19
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### Delete entry by entry_id and user_id
DELETE {{apiurl}}/entries
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "entry_id": 1,
  "user_id": 19
}


### Get Kubios data
GET {{apiurl}}/kubios/user-data
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### POST Kubios data to sql
POST {{apiurl}}/kubios/sql
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

#### Get Kubios data from sql
GET {{apiurl}}/kubios/sql/19
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



